{"tid":1904344,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[奶到惹肺炎]Google瑞士員工確診武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-29T14:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T05:56:51.000Z","uid":226155,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"036d189b77c5fdfa45ff5083832bdc80e46150f2","tid":1904344,"uid":226155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:30:23.000Z","msg":"A Google employee has tested positive for the coronavirus, and the company is further restricting its employee travel as concerns around the outbreak grow.<br />\n<br />\nOn Friday, the California-based search giant emailed its employees to inform them that an employee who had been in the Zurich office has tested positive for the virus, which causes the disease COVID-19, a source familiar with the matter told Business Insider. That employee was not symptomatic while in the office.<br />\n<br />\nGoogle is preventing employees from traveling to Iran, as well as two Italian regions where the virus is spreading, Lombardy and Veneto. From March 2, the company will also ban travel to South Korea and Japan.<br />\n<br />\nThe identity and condition of the Google employee who tested positive for the coronavirus is not known.<br />\n<br />\nIn a statement, a Google spokesperson said: &quot;We can confirm that one employee from our Zurich office has been diagnosed with the coronavirus. They were in the Zurich office for a limited time, before they had any symptoms. We have taken &mdash; and will continue to take &mdash; all necessary precautionary measures, following the advice of public health officials, as we prioritize everyone's health and safety.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nSince the coronavirus outbreak began in December, nearly 83,000 people have been infected, and more than 2,800 have died.<br />\n<br />\nGoogle is continuing to prohibit travel to China unless employees are returning home, and all international travel over the next 90 days will require review.<br />\n<br />\nCNN reporter Kerry Flynn also reported on Friday that Google was canceling its Google News Initiative Summit in the Bay Area, a conference geared toward the media industry."},{"pid":"7af01ca159f226f89dcc45df788abb1f11cc9c4a","tid":1904344,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdcaf6b67793e7247fdfd8de4d7b609cf773f9a2","tid":1904344,"uid":199501,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"多謝先知<br />\napple應該奶野了"},{"pid":"ab686727e7c52df8167c3dba93b281a1f1053cde","tid":1904344,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"大家睇到可唔可以入去幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n〖突發〗〖已FC〗多功能抗爭App 香城Online登陸IOS啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1904307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1904307</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"521efa251e78d93c2fb35f97b885900c3446e310","tid":1904344,"uid":226155,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"cdcaf6b67793e7247fdfd8de4d7b609cf773f9a2","tid":1904344,"uid":199501,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"多謝先知<br />\napple應該奶野了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-29T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"Apple 一月廿八已經禁止所有員工去中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGoogle一月廿九仲腿張開叫過左中國嘅員工快D返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c7d48be7c50a06b9a7bcf15485aab692f6195f","tid":1904344,"uid":29093,"like":20,"dislik